<div id="content">

<p>OneTime is under version control at <a
href="https://github.com/kfogel/OneTime"
>github.com/kfogel/OneTime</a> and at
<a href="https://gitorious.org/onetime"
>gitorious.org/onetime</a>.</p>

<p>The two are kept in sync; you can submit pull/merge requests at
either location.  Please use the GitHub repository for filing
issues.</p>

<p>OneTime is written in <a href="http://www.python.org/" >Python</a>.
Its <a href="onetime" >source code</a> is heavily commented; any
question you might have about design or implementation is probably
answered there.</p>

